\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula $\Question$
\end_inset

Assume 
\begin_inset Formula $A\in M_{n}(\F)$
\end_inset

 is positive definite.
 Prove that all its diagonal entries are real and positive.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\Answer$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 PD so 
\begin_inset Formula $\usub{\v e_{i}\H A\v e_{i}}{a_{ii}\in\R}{}{>0}$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $\v e_{i}\in\mathrm{basis_{\bot}}\left(A\right)$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Formula $\qed$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
